OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1777014326
OL,3,CFour teenagers arrested after man
OL,4,Ckilled in suspected hit-and-run
OL,6,FFour teenage boys have been arrested
OL,7,Fon suspicion of murder after a 44-year-
OL,8,Fold man was killed in a suspected hit-
OL,9,Fand-run in a town centre.
OL,11,FLocal man Matthew Weller died in
OL,12,Fhospital after being struck by a
OL,13,FVolkswagen Passat at the junction of
OL,14,FBlackburn Road and Birch Street in
OL,15,FAccrington shortly after 10pm on
OL,16,FWednesday, 22 April.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/4
