CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1777014326
OL,3,CFour teenagers arrested after man
OL,4,Ckilled in suspected hit-and-run
OL,6,FLancashire Police confirmed the
OL,7,Fvehicle involved failed to stop at the
OL,8,Fscene and it was later found abandoned
OL,9,Fon Barden Road. It has since been
OL,10,Frecovered for forensic examination.
OL,12,FOfficers have arrested three 17-year-
OL,13,Fold boys from Accrington and an 18-
OL,14,Fyear-old from Blackburn. All four
OL,15,Fremain in police custody for
OL,16,Fquestioning.
OL,18,FSpecially trained officers are
OL,19,Fcurrently supporting the victim's
OL,20,Ffamily as the investigation continues.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/4
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
