CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1777014326
OL,3,CFour teenagers arrested after man
OL,4,Ckilled in suspected hit-and-run
OL,6,F"I know that people in the community
OL,7,Fare shocked by last night's events but
OL,8,Fplease rest assured that we are doing
OL,9,Fall we can to establish what has
OL,10,Fhappened and to find those responsible
OL,11,Ffor this man's death."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/4
